original_title: アンジュルム 上國料萌衣バースデーイベント2020
overview: ANGERME Kamikokuryo Moe Birthday Event 2020 (アンジュルム 上國料萌衣バースデーイベント2020) was Kamikokuryo Moe's 21st birthday event. It took place on October 26, 2020 with two shows at LANDMARK HALL.  In compliance with government policy due to the coronavirus pandemic, cheering, crowding, standing, and closeness in the venue were prohibited, and wearing masks was required to enter.  From October 26 to October 27, 2020, a recording of the event was digitally distributed to fanclub members who apply.
title: ANGERME Kamikokuryo Moe Birthday Event 2020
